    "Ans.1 Dictionaries keys are needed to be immutable as, if the keys are changed then thier values will be become irrelvent of their context. \n",
    "For example:- if the key named \"name\" is to be changed with other key like \"subject\", then the value of the key \"Mohit\" will become irrelevent and doesn't make any sense.\n"
